<header>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1><%= link_to "Generic Webnotes", root_path %></h1>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="headerLine"></div>

<div id="center">
  <p>This is a web app that allows you to save notes online, without requiring an account.</p>
  <p>This app is not intended to be used for confidential information, anybody who knows the unique key for your notepad will be able to view and edit it freely.</p> <br>
  <p>Entering an identifer that is not in use will create a new notepad for you to store notes. If the identifer has already been used, you will be directed to the existing notepad. You may store up to 32 notes per notepad.</p> <br>
  <p>Try entering an identifier only you would think of, or click 'Go' with the suggested identifier to get started right away.</p><br>

  <%= form_for @notepad do |f| %>
    <p>
      <%= f.label "Enter the Notepad Identifier:" %><br>
      <%= f.text_field :url, size: "30", placeholder: @notepad.url, value: "" %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :orig_url, size: "0", value: @notepad.url %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= f.submit "Go" %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
